See reasoning in https://github.com/istanbuljs/istanbuljs/pull/743#discussion_r1496887454 and https://github.com/istanbuljs/istanbuljs/pull/685#discussion_r887426322.

This will enable us to switch to `TraceMap` without any test failures.

container hits, because the statement map entries do not contain a "loc"
field, they just have this inforation at the top level.
